OL,3,CEx Kent police officer admits fraud
OL,4,Cusing horse racing syndicate
OL,6,FA former Kent Police officer has
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to defrauding members
OL,8,Fof a horse racing betting syndicate.
OL,10,FMichael Stanley, who headed the Layezy
OL,11,FRacing group, operated a "fraudulent
OL,12,FPonzi scheme" and misused his clients'
OL,13,Fmoney between 2013 and 2019, a court
OL,14,Fheard.
