OL,3,CEx Kent police officer admits fraud
OL,4,Cusing horse racing syndicate
OL,6,FThe 67-year-old, who used to be a
OL,7,Fsergeant with Kent Police, was
OL,8,Farrested in August 2019 and was later
OL,9,Fcharged with dishonestly making false
OL,10,Frepresentations to members of the
OL,11,FLayezy Racing Syndicate, knowingly
OL,12,Frunning a business for a fraudulent
OL,13,Fpurpose contrary to the Fraud Act
OL,14,F2006, and three counts of knowingly
OL,15,Frunning a business for a fraudulent
OL,16,Fpurpose contrary to the Companies Act
OL,17,F2006.
OL,19,FHe pleaded guilty to all five offences
OL,20,Fat Sevenoaks Magistrates' Court on
OL,21,FThursday.
