OL,3,CEx Kent police officer admits fraud
OL,4,Cusing horse racing syndicate
OL,6,FProsecutor Amanda Burrows said:
OL,7,F"Between at least 2013 and February
OL,8,F2019, the defendant operated a
OL,9,Ffraudulent Ponzi scheme and the scheme
OL,10,Finvolved an operation of a betting
OL,11,Fsyndicate called the Layezy Racing
OL,12,FSyndicate (LRS)."
OL,14,FMs Burrows said the LRS was supposed
OL,15,Fto have been a scheme whereby members
OL,16,Finvested funds for which a small
OL,17,Fproportion was to be used for
OL,18,F"gambling collectively", which was
OL,19,Fcontrolled by Stanley.
