OL,3,CEx Kent police officer admits fraud
OL,4,Cusing horse racing syndicate
OL,6,FIt was "marketed as being virtually
OL,7,Frisk free", Ms Burrows said.
OL,9,FStanley claimed he was carrying out
OL,10,Fsuccessful gambling with horses but
OL,11,F"lied" to members about the amount of
OL,12,Fsuccess he was having, and
OL,13,F"deliberately concealed" that he was
OL,14,Fnot operating the scheme in accordance
OL,15,Fwith its rules, the court heard.
