OL,3,CEx Kent police officer admits fraud
OL,4,Cusing horse racing syndicate
OL,6,FHe admitted dishonestly making false
OL,7,Frepresentations to members of the
OL,8,FLayezy Racing Syndicate, namely that
OL,9,Feach member's funds, having been paid
OL,10,Finto the syndicate, were available for
OL,11,Fwithdrawal on notice.
OL,13,FAlso, that the reported increase in
OL,14,Fthe value of each member's fund
OL,15,Fresulted from successful gambling
OL,16,F"carried out, controlled, and or
OL,17,Fdirected" by Stanley, according to the
OL,18,Fcharges.
