OL,3,CEx Kent police officer admits fraud
OL,4,Cusing horse racing syndicate
OL,6,FHe also pleaded guilty to four charges
OL,7,Fof knowingly running a business for a
OL,8,Ffraudulent purpose, with one count
OL,9,Fcontrary to the Fraud Act 2006 and
OL,10,Fthree contrary to the Companies Act
OL,11,F2006.
OL,13,FOf the latter three counts, the first
OL,14,Frelates to the running of Layezy Ltd,
OL,15,Fthe second to Layezy Racing Ltd and
OL,16,Fthe third to Number 1 Guide Ltd.
