OL,3,CEx Kent police officer admits fraud
OL,4,Cusing horse racing syndicate
OL,6,FAll four charges said Stanley misused
OL,7,Fmoney held in the betting scheme for
OL,8,F"personal gain" and to "fund members'
OL,9,Fwithdrawals that included profits to
OL,10,Fwhich they were not entitled".
OL,12,FStanley, of Walderslade, Kent, was
OL,13,Fbailed on conditions to appear at
OL,14,FMaidstone Crown Court at a later date
OL,15,Ffor sentence.
